title: Terror During Golf Season
description:
We revisit Justin's request to being an associate producer (00:07:12). Kirk is not impressed at all with Brandon Walker's golf skills or his defense of Trysta Krick over a harmless prank call (00:36:35). A Kingston family wins $5 million for the terror they face living on a golf course (00:42:06). Boston Magazine ranks the most influential Bostonians and it turns out that many of them are absolute nobodies (01:00:00). Mazz as a muppet on Cameo, Chris isn't fooling anyone with 'Me & the Nominees' & much more.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/kminshow
